 in line with the absence of jet flapping in this\ndirection. Furthermore, the leading SPOD eigenvalues turn out to be, at least,\ntwo orders of magnitude larger than higher-order eigenvalues, suggesting\npotential of reduced-order models for the twin-jet screech.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 May 2021 07:15:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Apr 2022 13:47:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 23:04:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-25"}
