om C times E(K_s-V)/E(B-V) has C\n= -1.14 and a scatter of $\\sim$7%. Using the IRAC 5.6 micron band instead of\nK_s gives C = -1.03 and the least scatter of $\\sim$3\\%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 May 2021 14:41:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 May 2021 18:28:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
